window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Prince of Time</i> is Book Two in the After Cilmeri Series: </p> <p>Two teenagers are catapulted back in time to alter history and save the medieval kingdom of Wales... </p> <p>David and his man-at-arms, Ieuan, find themselves alone and on the run from a company of English soldiers who've sworn vengeance for the recent death of their king. Meanwhile, Llywelyn lays on his deathbed, wounded by a traitor's arrow. And once again, it is David and Anna, and all that they represent, that holds the key to the survival of Wales. </p> <p><i>Prince of Time</i> is the second book in the After Cilmeri series.</p>"; 
